short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Boost your Etsy™ SEO with Etsy™ Tag Finder Chrome extension. Best tag optimization tool. Find & analyze tags efficiently.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Etsy Tag Finder is a robust Chrome extension that provides you valuable insights for optimizing etsy SEO tag strategy and outperforming your competitors. 

  

Key Features:  

>> Instantly access competitors' tags and keywords directly from Etsy. 
>> Real-time search results at your fingertips. 
>> View tag performance metrics including frequency, views, favorites, competition, and sales. 
>> Integration with Google Trends for trend analysis.  
>> Bulk copy or export Etsy tags to a convenient CSV format. 
>> Save time by easily organizing and analyzing your tag data.  

 

How to Use?  

>> Install the extension  
>> Click on the extension icon to Activate   
>> Once installed, you'll see the Etsy Tag Finder icon in your Chrome browser. 
>> Click the icon to open the extension and visit the website 
>> Click on tag extractor option to extract the etsy tags  

Keep an eye out for the upcoming Etsy Tags Generator feature to further enhance your Etsy shop's tag optimization. 

  

Etsy Tag extractor empowers both new and existing sellers to make data-driven decisions. 

Improve your Etsy shop's visibility and performance using these valuable tag insights.
